{"type": "article", "id": 30703, "title": "模块型家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160807230228JlIWpPOqdYHn1Q0x.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>阿根廷建筑师及设计师 <a href=\"http://www.nataliageci.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Natalia Geci</a> 希望可以为那些因为各处奔波而居无定所、每次搬家都会苦恼家具去处的人们创造一种更符合他们“这种游牧型”生活方式的家具。这个名为 LYNKO 的模块型家具系列包含架子、托盘、钩子等组件，能够同可折叠的金属框架、木制铰链以及收纳袋自由组合在一起，打造出小型的办公区、梳妆台，甚至是一间厨房。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230243eKUXn2y7PbIAOEd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.151667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230243ShCwvtqR9k7Oj0XN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230243hZlEM9PqYXTHQdK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807230243W26dAmZwbhJaG8Ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}